title: Leah Remini is a Troublemaker (Part 1: Full Blown Scientology)
description: This week we dove head first into the world of Scientology. Before we can even talk about getting out we need to talk about how Leah Remini ended up in this wild ass cult from the age of 11. You may only recognize Leah Remini from King of Queens but she knows Tom Cruise.
